snippet.title: Official Trailer - Midnight Cinderella: Ikémen Royal Romances (Otome Game)
snippet.description:
Fall in love with the prince of your dreams in Midnight Cinderella, the Otome Game for iOS and Android downloaded by 3 million women around the world!

AppStore:http://ow.ly/FM3I2 
Googleplay： http://ow.ly/LTwhK 
Amazon App Store：http://ow.ly/LTwiV 

【 Story 】
You, a commoner, have now become princess of an entire country!
The role of "princess" is to find the prince who will rule beside her.
You can only pick one king.
Who will be the next king of Wysteria?!

Get the latest updates and meet the princes of Wysteria on our Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/CyMidnightCinderella
